data.description: Did someone say NO HOA? You'll fall in love with this luminous Lawrence Township beauty. Beautiful home is tucked into a country setting with spectacular views of Fort Harrison State Park. Vaulted wood beamed ceilings. Open, airy layout. Serene three-season porch. Amazing location—convenient to restaurants, shopping, and an easy commute to anywhere in the metro Indy area. Thoughtful updates include bamboo flooring, remodeled sunroom, tiled shower, exterior paint. You'll love sitting by your cozy fire this winter & the fenced-in yard with is perfect for pets or humans to frolic freely.All this plus: Prestigious,award-winning Lawrence Township public schools and early childhood learning centers and renowned for music education. Also: No HOA!
